title: Dr. Leana Wen: "Lifelines"
description: Michael's conversation with Dr. Leana Wen, author of "Lifelines: A Doctor's Journey in the Fight for Public Health." She is the former Baltimore, MD health commissioner and a CNN and Washington Post contributor. Original air date 10 August 2021. The book was published on 27 July 2021.
author: podcasts@siriusxm.com (Leana Wen, Michael Smerconish)
